parameters.name: アコースティック・田舎・のどか・クギターメイン

parameters:
--Several days ago. In the evening at the "Fortress City of
Anatos" in the Tar-Za region.
\n<Sentry A>"--and that's when I said it!"
\n<Sentry B>"Seriously? You've got guts, man."

\n<Sentry B>"...But man, it's boring. Can't the shift change come any
sooner?"

\n<Sentry A>"Just a little longer to bear.... Ah, that reminds me, isn't
it about time for the regular delivery from Annabern?"

\n<Sentry B>"Oh yeah, today's the day for that. Totally slipped my
mind."
\n<Sentry B>"...Oh. Speak of the devil."

\n<Sentry A>"Alright, alright, good work. The regular delivery from
Annabern, right? Show me your permit."
\n<Merchant>"Yes, here it is."

\n<Merchant>"But really, shouldn't I be on a face pass by now? I've been
doing this for years, you know?"

\n<Sentry A>"That's something you need to take up with the management
office. They're strict about these things.... Alright,
you're good to go."
\n<Merchant>"Thank you very much."

\n<Sentry B>"...So, is this the last one for today? Let's just hurry up
and switch out."

\n<Sentry A>"Yeah.... Right, how about we go for a drink tonight? It's
half-price ale night at our usual spot."

\n<Sentry B>"You've got a good memory for the important stuff. Alright,
let's go drinking tonight then."
\n<Sentry A>"...Hey, did you hear that?"
\n<Sentry B>"You're joking...!"

parameters.name: 猛獣の鳴き声（中くらいのうなり声）

parameters: \n<Sentry B>"Monsters! Did they follow the cargo?!"
\n<Sentry A>"Who cares about that! Let's do this!"

\n<Sentry A>"...Phew. It's rare for monsters to show up. Did we have
some tasty food in the cargo or something?"
\n<Sentry B>"Who knows... Anyway, let's head back and report--"
\n<Sentry B>"--Huh...?"
\n<Sentry A>"What is this... What's going on...?"

parameters.name: 恐怖・重厚・不安・不気味な感じ

parameters: \n<Sentry A>"What is this... What is this...?!"
\n<Sentry A>"Aaaaahhhhhhh!! Monsters! There's a horde of them!!"

parameters.name: 猛獣の鳴き声（低いうなり声）

parameters: \n<Sentry B>"Guards!! Someone come help!! Anyone!! Anybodyyyyy!!"
